			<p>All API access is over HTTPS and accessed from https://encrypt.to/api/v1/. All data is sent and received as JSON.</p>
			<br />
			<h3>Client errors</h3>
			<pre>curl https://encrypt.to/api/v1/keyserver/lookup</pre>
			<pre>{"status":"error","message":"Wrong params, please try again."}</pre>
			<br />
			<h3>Get public key by email</h3>
			<pre>curl https://encrypt.to/api/v1/keyserver/lookup?email=hello@encrypt.to</pre>
			<pre>{"status":"success","keys":[{"key_id":"0x11489A1F","public_key":"-----BEGIN PGP PUBLIC KEY BLOCK-----"}]}</pre>
			<br />
			<h3>Get public key by key id</h3>
			<pre>curl https://encrypt.to/api/v1/keyserver/lookup?keyid=0x11489A1F</pre>			
			<pre>{"status":"success","keys":[{"key_id":"0x11489A1F","public_key":"-----BEGIN PGP PUBLIC KEY BLOCK-----"}]}</pre>	
